<< methods Handle set >>

properties

Returns the properties name of an object handle.

Syntax

properties(h)
c = properties(h)

Input argument

h

a handle object

Output argument

c

a cell of strings

Description

properties returns a cell of strings with properties name.

See also

isprop.

History

Version Description
1.0.0 initial version

Author
